{"tid":1136642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(又係肥閪) 借肥閪表演為防癌會籌錢 郭敦誠終極「走數」善款下落不明","createTime":"2019-05-03T06:54:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-03T07:16:23.000Z","uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0ce1100720b81eb8933d4ece6b83f8d51c0fc27a","tid":1136642,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T06:54:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190503/59558473\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190503%2F59558473&d=YcIJTvf9PmU%2BR6jslv3gjNOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=2308329c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190503%2F59558473&h=3f934ce7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190503/59558473</a><br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》早前報道，藝人肥閪（Maria Cordero）去年10月舉行慈善晚宴，為香港防癌會籌錢。惟主辦單位「尊位集團」一直拖欠百萬善款，並兩次要求延期找數。防癌會提出4月30日是最終期限，但尊位負責人郭敦誠終極「走數」，防癌會指直至5月1日仍未收到款項，徵詢法律意見及商議後，會將事件交由律師處理及跟進。  <br />\n<br />\n尊位集團在2018年10月舉辦《最好的時代慈善晚宴2018》，邀請香港防癌會為受惠機構。根據簽訂文件，尊位集團會於活動兩個月內捐贈善款，事件至今已半年，公司亦爆出財困欠薪。  <br />\n<br />\n肥閪早前接受訪問稱，當晚晚宴賣枱分一圍3萬、5萬和10萬元，賣枱收益逾百萬元，善款由尊位集團保管，大嘆自己遇人不淑。記者3月曾致電郭敦誠，當時他稱善款只是延遲轉交，強調無問題。記者今日再致電郭，但電話號碼已停止服務。&nbsp; <br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，郭敦誠曾任尊位集團有限公司董事，但持有的股份已在2017年9月28日轉讓予袁少中，同日辭任尊位董事。袁少中接任公司董事後，在2018年8月14日將股份轉讓予一間註冊地點在薩摩亞的「尊位控股有限公司」。"},{"pid":"f20beacfcd78f64dc983ccbcc36e2e44d86cd289","tid":1136642,"uid":61954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T06:56:30.000Z","msg":"我冇睇錯！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8e1377e3fd7c578b990febb18a7b4a830106401","tid":1136642,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T07:03:33.000Z","msg":"藝人肥閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25fced76e784a1f00f79e115755adc9462cade0d","tid":1136642,"uid":22422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T07:12:24.000Z","msg":"肥閪點解唔躝去大灣區唱校歌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e215d0df9e40bcab2780c4c500fa2bb95b029a94","tid":1136642,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T07:16:23.000Z","msg":"騙徒"}]}